{"tid":955547,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★No IT] 挖礦機生產廠商比特大陸(Bitmain)據報大幅裁員達五成","createTime":"2018-12-25T13:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T03:54:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"16f8c5a0d6cab985303de798431f6f33c15657c9","tid":955547,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:33:36.000Z","msg":"內媒體報道，於9月上載招股書，擬在港上市的虛擬貨幣挖礦機生產廠商比特大陸(Bitmain)，近日傳出<span style=\"color: red;\">大幅裁員的消息。更有消息人士稱，裁員規模達五成。</span><br />\n<br />\n報道又引述比特大陸員工稱，公司確實於近期開始裁員；另外，最近幾個月員工的出差預算審核也變得嚴格，更被要求盡量縮減開支。<br />\n<br />\n另外，亦有以色列媒體Globes報道，比特大陸兩年前在當地開設的研發中心已關閉，全部23名員工都將被辭退，而負責領導研發中心的比特大陸副總裁Gadi Glikberg也將離職。<br />\n<br />\n惟比特大陸向內地媒體回應傳聞時稱，傳聞不實，並指公司是據業務發展情況進行年末正常人員調整，未來也一如既往歡迎各界人才的加盟。<br />\n<br />\n近期由於比特幣現金(Bitcoin Cash)硬分叉引發虛擬貨幣大冧市，比特幣失守四千美元大關。有不少礦工亦因掘礦變得無利可圖，拋售礦機套現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181225/bkn-20181225201433678-1225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181225%2Fbkn-20181225201433678-1225_00842_001.html&d=EAYqXrIIJPGx4S0IDbeNMv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=3ee745ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181225/bkn-20181225201433678-1225_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"aec4ecb9c9de47f386c794e1fdedad9670a06d69","tid":955547,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d775ace5fdd4c064e8cb95ae42db89f838d61e1","tid":955547,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T13:34:35.000Z","msg":"今日香港IT大賣廣告，入行可致富！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/953462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/953462</a>"}